created: 2025-04-18, last updated: 2026-03-28, [Read more](https://deepwiki.com/wasp-lang/wasp/4.1-syntax-and-features&rut=097df24598a30596e85ce5039400b812640d3c8962220b8dc6bbab222f6145e7)

```
// Define a query that fetches data
query myQuery {
fn: import { myQueryFn } from "@src/server/queries/myQuery.js",
entities: [User, Task] // Entities accessed by this query
}
// Define an action that modifies data
action myAction {
fn: import { myActionFn } from "@src/server/actions/myAction.js",
entities: [User]
}
```
…
### CRUD Operations
Automatic CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations for entities:
```
crud tasks {
entity: Task,
operations: {
get: {},
getAll: {},
create: {},
update: {},
delete: {}
}
}
```
…
|Declaration|Purpose|Required Properties|Optional Properties|
|--|--|--|--|
|`job`|Defines background task|`executor`, `perform`|`schedule`, `entities`|
|`api`|Defines custom API endpoint|`fn`, `httpRoute`|`middlewareConfigFn`, `auth`|
|`apiNamespace`|Groups related APIs|`path`|`middlewareConfigFn`|
|`crud`|Generates CRUD operations|`entity`, `operations`|-|

